transform_def.name: designed_3rd15
transform_def.string: let r = 1 / length(p_in) r1 = 2 / length(p_in) r2 = 0.5 / length(p_in) a1 = exp(abs(tan(p_in.x))) * twoinvpi() a2 = fmod(exp((abs(p_in.y) + abs(p_in.x)) * invpi()), tanh(abs(p_in.y)) + abs(p_in.x)) * tanh(p_in.x * p_in.y) * exp(cos(abs(p_in.x))) a = fmod(a2, a1) b1 = exp(cos(abs(sin(p_in.x)))) b2 = tan(abs(sin(p_in.x)) + cos(abs(p_in.y) + abs(p_in.x))) b = fmod(b1, b2) z = if r < invpi() then fmod(b, a) else if r < twoinvpi() then fmod(abs(p_in.x) * twopi(), a2) else fmod(tan(p_in.x * p_in.y * fourpi()), b2) con0 = abs(z) > r1 con1 = abs(z) < r1 && abs(z) > r2 con2 = abs(z) < r2 in (if if fill <= 0.0 then con0 else if fill > 0.25 then con2 else con1 then p_in else vec2(0.0)) * weight
